OL,3,CTories fined #10,000 for failing to
OL,4,Caccurately declare donations
OL,6,Fhave been fined more than #10,000 by
OL,7,Fthe elections watchdog for failing to
OL,8,Faccurately declare party donations
OL,9,Fover a three-year period.
OL,11,FThe party under-reported non-cash
OL,12,Fdonations in the form of a member of
OL,13,Fstaff seconded to the party by long-
OL,14,Ftime Tory donor, Richard Harpin,
OL,15,Fbetween April 2020 and December 2023.
OL,17,FMr Harpin, founder of home repairs
OL,18,Fcompany HomeServe and review website
OL,19,FCheckatrade, has provided the party
OL,20,Fwith almost #3 million in cash and non-
OL,21,Fcash donations since 2008.
