OL,3,CTories fined #10,000 for failing to
OL,4,Caccurately declare donations
OL,6,FIn total, the party under-reported the
OL,7,Fdonations by more than #200,000 when
OL,8,Fthe employee went from part-time to
OL,9,Ffull-time work, and subsequently
OL,10,Freported a single non-cash donation
OL,11,Frelating to the same employee in
OL,12,FDecember 2023.
OL,14,FThe party insisted it was due to an
OL,15,F"administrative error" and was "not
OL,16,Fdeliberate". It paid two fines
OL,17,Ftotalling #10,750 on March 6.
