OL,3,CTories fined #10,000 for failing to
OL,4,Caccurately declare donations
OL,6,FIt is the largest fine paid by the
OL,7,FConservatives since December 2021,
OL,8,Fwhen the party was fined #17,800 for
OL,9,Ffailing to deliver an accurate
OL,10,Fquarterly donation report and failing
OL,11,Fto keep accurate accounting records.
OL,13,FDirector of regulation and digital
OL,14,Ftransformation at the Electoral
OL,15,FCommission, Louise Edwards, said: "The
OL,16,Fpolitical finance laws we enforce are
OL,17,Fthere to ensure transparency in how
OL,18,Fparties are funded and to increase
OL,19,Fpublic confidence in our system, so
OL,20,Fit's important donations are fully and
OL,21,Fclearly reported.
