OL,6,F"Where we find offences, we carefully
OL,7,Fconsider the circumstances before
OL,8,Fdeciding whether to impose a sanction.
OL,9,FWe take into account a range of
OL,10,Ffactors before making our final
OL,11,Fdecision, including proportionality."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Conservative
OL,14,FParty said: "After becoming aware of
OL,15,Fan administrative error, the party
OL,16,Fself-reported to the Electoral
OL,17,FCommission.
OL,19,F"We accept its findings and appreciate
OL,20,Fthat the Electoral Commission accepts
OL,21,Fthat this was not deliberate."
